rn the bronze.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Katie Ledecky won the gold in the 800 free for the fourth-straight Olympics, while Australia's Ariarne Titmus took silver.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9998155945131256, \"rank\": 0.00017218375788060817, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2175, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u0089 \\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0081\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0091\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u008e\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u008d\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0099\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0084 \\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u008c\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0084\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0083\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0080\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u008b\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0088\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0092\\u00f0\\u009d\\u0090\\u0093 \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u0089Paige Madden drops 5.48 seconds off her PR to finish third in the 800 Free with a time of 8:13.00 \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#OlympiansMadeHere|#Paris2024|#GoHoospic.twitter.com/cfG1vis0pl  Finally, first-time Olympian Gretchen Walsh won her third 